name: Sacrilegious at Moms House
description:
This is a quick self portrait I took in my moms backyard.  This headdress had sold and I wanted a picture of it, so I stripped down, put on my black eye shadow, and ran out to catch the last rays of the setting sun.  Luckily I have grown up in an environment that nurtured my creative side, so such activities are praised in my family.  

Photo, Model and Costume Bubbles And Frown
